<br>
&quot;Live long little spotted one...&quot;<br>
<br>
::with another smile at the young deer Shey jumped down out of the tree and continued on through the forest looking for diffrent prey to catch.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 350<br> <font color=#993300>(6/10/01 4:05:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=17>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> *several days later (for Hipp)</span><hr size=1> The talons dug into the chest of the bear, but bear swatted at her like a play thing.  The small amazon being flung into the large trunk of a tree with a hard thud.  The breath being knocked out of her she slowely got up as the bear growled and moved down to all fours.  Beginning to move slowely move towards Hippolyte.  Again, she stood there watching it move towards her.  Ready...she would calculate this move...and could not let the bear get the best of her.  The bear stopped and growled again at her.  As it did, Hipp deciding it might be more into the growl and not expect moved in a quick slash her talong dagger slicing thru it's neck.  The bear again sliced at her, leaving deep marks in her thigh.  The blood beginning to ooze out and down her leg.  She hissed at the bear and her other arm slashed down on the other side...the bear gasping as the harpi talon sunk deep.   It jerked back, ripping the daggers from their hold.  It again growled..but a more bloody gurgling growl....again standing on it's back legs.  Hipp rushed and again dug the talon's deep into the chest...until they met their deep inbedded mark.  Her hand deep inside the bear, she twisted the talon in his heart muscle.  This quickly stopping the heart and the bear falling forward on top of the queen. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umarpeamzn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Marpe Amzn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#993300>(6/19/01 5:25:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> respect</span><hr size=1> After taking the life from the wild hog, Marpe does the small blessing and thanks ceremony.  With the blood she crosses her cheeks and forehead.  Then takes the bit of meat from the hog and eats it.  The amazon then laid down beside the hog and closed her eyes.  She began to chant a slow rhythmic chant to Artemis and then slipped into a vision quest.  Her body still beside the hog. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 120<br> <font color=#993300>(6/19/01 8:05:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=214.topic&index=32>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hunt</span><hr size=1> Alysia took her dagger and cut the mountain lion open, a breeze flew by as she pulled out the heart of the creature and sank her teeth into it. It was tradition, it was ritual. She then looked at her blood covered hands as she swallowed the meat.<br>
